":[{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I just moved in across the street. （我刚从街对面搬过来。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Well, welcome to our neighbourhood.（噢，欢迎来到我们社"},{"type":"text","text":"区。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Are you just getting back from the party? Did you enjoy yourself?"},{"type":"text","text":"（你刚从聚会回来？玩得开心吗？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Yeah, it was great. So much fun. （是的，棒极了。很有意"},{"type":"text","text":"思。）"}]}]}